Ri Mu Hyeok's watch?

627
00:39:12,851 --> 00:39:14,561
We searched his residence, the camp,

628
00:39:15,144 --> 00:39:17,522
and everyone he knew,

629
00:39:18,523 --> 00:39:19,941
