662
00:41:28,653 --> 00:41:29,696
Why is she here?

663
00:41:29,779 --> 00:41:32,323
What is Captain Ri hiding?

664
00:41:32,407 --> 00:41:35,451
What is he scheming at home
with his subordinates

665
00:41:35,785 --> 00:41:38,371
under the excuse
