677
00:42:19,787 --> 00:42:21,164
You sly motherfucker.

678
00:42:27,295 --> 00:42:31,007
Captain Ri, can't you see that I am
in the middle of an investigation?

679
00:42:31,591 --> 00:42:32,759
Get out.

680
00:42:39,348 --> 00:42:42,769
