wouldn't tell the truth.

684
00:42:52,278 --> 00:42:53,696
I think differently.

685
00:42:53,780 --> 00:42:56,032
Only the man who is directly involved
can tell the truth.

686
00:42:56,616 --> 00:42:57,575
Thus,

687
00:43:00,078 --> 00:43:02,455
go and tell the truth about the things

688
00:43:03,081 --> 00:43:04,415
you have done.

689
00:43:05,083 --> 00:43:06,876
What are you talking about?

690
00:43:16,427 --> 00:43:17,470
Hello.

691
00:43:18,930 --> 00:43:20,306
Senior Colonel.

692
00:43:20,389 --> 00:43:21,891
What is the meaning of this?

693
00:43:22,391 --> 00:43:25,103
Didn't you wrap up
the truck accident already?

694
00:43:26,062 --> 00:43:29,357
I received an official request
from the State Security Department

695
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:33,319
to send the drivers and you.

696
00:43:33,820 --> 00:43:36,781
But why do they want me as well?

697
00:43:36,864 --> 00:43:38,199
I am not involved in any way!

698
00:43:38,282 --> 00:43:41,285
<i>Didn't you promise to take</i>
<i>full responsibility?</i>

699
00:43:41,494 --> 00:43:43,996
<i>Why do I need to be summoned?</i>

700
00:43:44,580 --> 00:43:45,873
<i>Come to my room right away!</i>

701
00:43:47,083 --> 00:43:48,584
Listen, Ri Jeong Hyeok.

702
00:43:48,668 --> 00:43:49,836
