739
00:45:48,871 --> 00:45:50,623
My father.

740
00:45:50,706 --> 00:45:52,416
Your father is a great man.

741
00:45:52,917 --> 00:45:54,085
But

742
00:45:54,627 --> 00:45:56,879
the world isn't a flower field.

743
00:45:57,463 --> 00:45:59,840
You shouldn't be good to people
who beat you up.

744
00:46:00,508 --> 00:46:03,261
Those who throw punches don't know
how much it hurts.

745
00:46:04,220 --> 00:46:06,013
Only those who take punches do.

746
00:46:07,056 --> 00:46:08,933
If someone tries to harass you,

747
00:46:09,809 --> 00:46:11,894
throw a punch first.

748
00:46:12,478 --> 00:46:14,313
